      "body" : "This isn&#39;t 100% true. <code>Comparable.class.isAssignableFrom(Byte.class) == true</code> but <code>Byte.class.isInstance(Comparable.class) == false</code>. In other words, <code>isInstance()</code> is not symmetric for interfaces, only for subclasses."
