      "body" : "@Gili: You&#39;ve got it a bit wrong there. <code>Byte.class.isInstance(Comparable.class)</code> is false because a <code>Class</code> object is not an instance of <code>Byte</code>. The correct comparison to <code>Comparable.class.isAssignableFrom(Byte.class)</code> is <code>Comparable.class.isInstance((byte) 1)</code>, which is true."
