      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Technicality: If <code>obj</code> is <code>null</code> then <code>clazz.isAssignableFrom(obj.getClass()) == clazz.isInstance(obj)</code> will throw a <code>NullPointerException</code> and not return <code>true</code>."
