  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3949260/java-class-isinstance-vs-class-isassignablefrom",
  "title" : "java: Class.isInstance vs Class.isAssignableFrom",
  "body" : "<p>Let <code>clazz</code> be some <code>Class</code> and <code>obj</code> be some <code>Object</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Is</p>\n\n<pre><code>clazz.isAssignableFrom(obj.getClass())\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>always the same as</p>\n\n<pre><code>clazz.isInstance(obj)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>?</p>\n\n<p>If not, what are the differences?</p>\n"
